text: Caspar Einem (6 May 1948 - 9 September 2021) was an Austrian politician and businessman. He was a board member of Jetalliance. Einem was born in Salzburg, Austria. He was a member of the Social Democratic Party. Einem was the Minister of the Interior from 1995 until 1997. From 2000 until 2007, he was a member of the National Council. Einem died on 9 September 2021 in Vienna, Austria at the age of 73.Ehemaliger Innen- und Wissenschaftsminister Caspar Einem gestorben ==References== ==Other websites== * Caspar Einem's homepage * The Austrian Parliament on Caspar Einem Category:1948 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Austrian politicians Category:Austrian businesspeople
